CONTEXT scheduler_ctx
SETS
    TASKS, PROCESSORS
CONSTANTS
    task_priority, processor_speed
AXIOMS
    @axm1 task_priority ∈ TASKS → ℕ1
    @axm2 processor_speed ∈ PROCESSORS → ℕ1
    @axm3 card(PROCESSORS) > 0
    @axm4 ∀t1,t2·t1 ∈ TASKS ∧ t2 ∈ TASKS ⇒ (task_priority(t1) = task_priority(t2) ⇒ t1 = t2)
END
